Glencore Buys AMCI Warrior’s Optimum Coal Stake, Extra Shares to Own 14.1%

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-08-29T11:31:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-29/glencore-buys-amci-warrior-s-optimum-coal-stake-extra-shares-to-own-14-1-.html
Glencore International Plc acquired
AMCI Warrior Mauritius’s stake in  Optimum Coal Holdings (OPT)  Ltd. as
well as some shares in the open market to give it a 14.1 percent
stake in the Johannesburg-based coal producer, Jacques de Bie,
an external spokesman for Optimum, said by phone from  Cape Town 
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  